{"tid":1016692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次真係GTR 不過都係炒 on9 仔","createTime":"2019-02-11T01:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T09:49:38.000Z","uid":164501,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d107f19c016c87c480025881f8066aaac2cc7e71","tid":1016692,"uid":164501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:59:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190210/59244906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190210%2F59244906&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo5%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=b4a80982\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190210%2F59244906&h=ec1c50b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190210/59244906</a><br />\n<br />\n大埔發生嚴重交通意外，晚上近10時，據報一部日產Skyline跑車於安祥路往大元邨方向行駛，駛至安慈路交界，意外撞倒一名過路的50歲姓陳男子，他重傷倒卧地上，事後由救護車送往沙田威爾斯醫院搶救，情況危殆。警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n有車輛事發時駛經上址拍下意外經過，據車Cam所見，涉事的Skyline駛經燈位時，交通燈為綠燈，剛巧一名男子步出馬路，25歲姓趙司機收掣不及撞向過路男，他涉嫌危險駕駛引致他人身體受嚴重傷害被捕，已獲准保釋候查，下月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n睇車cam 好明顯GTR 當自己車神 係town 地板油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0f85b93fd5c3de795d38f3568bdad0d07b26fa","tid":1016692,"uid":169498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"老豆 我要買GTR"},{"pid":"a215d2657405feb1e27a6287c74e44f9cfdf8d05","tid":1016692,"uid":144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"個女人又嗌乜鳩 聽聲都想打撚鑊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3faa09a47f19c768b882aacd894c5f1eefc1cb","tid":1016692,"uid":56138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:09:41.000Z","msg":"2個戇